OL,7, Trudie Goodwin, alias The Bill's       
OL,8, Sergeant June Ackland is known for her 
OL,9,Cdoggedness in pursuit of baddiesG- a   
OL,10, trait very true to her real life...    
OL,12, "I can't stand baddies," she reveals.  
OL,13, "And the worst kind of baddies as far  
OL,14, as I'm concerned areCeco-killers.      
OL,15, People and institutions who have no    
OL,16, regard for the environment.            
OL,18, "In my mind these people areCcriminals 
OL,19, and should be locked up for good!"     
