OL,7, Brought-up during the '60s, Trudie     
OL,8, Goodwin says she'sC"an old hippie at   
OL,9,Cheart".                                
OL,11, "That whole era was about love and     
OL,12, peace. I suppose it was then that I    
OL,13, really took on board the issues that   
OL,14, would affect not only my future but    
OL,15,Cthe future of generations to come.     
OL,17, "Nuclear power, deforestation: the list
OL,18, goes on and on and it appears as       
OL,19, though very fewCrealise the dangers."  
