OL,5,CTRUDIE GOODWIN                Wx}}b4  
OL,6,                             W`~    
OL,7, "In my own way, I'm an eco-warrior,"   
OL,8, laughs Trudie Goodwin. "In the early   
OL,9, days I was out there on the streets in 
OL,10, the bigCGreenpeace marchesGcampaigning 
OL,11, for nuclear disarmament.               
OL,13, "I'm a terrible complainer, I'm        
OL,14, constantlyCwriting letters to the      
OL,15,CGovernmentGsounding off about things   
OL,16, like fuel emissions and so on.         
OL,18, "I'm also a great believer that to act 
OL,19, globally, you have toCact locally."    
