OL,5,CTRUDIE GOODWIN                Wx}}b4  
OL,6,                             W`~    
OL,7, "As a member ofCReclaim The Streets,   
OL,8, I'm very much in favour of ridding the 
OL,9, streets of cars and lorries," says     
OL,10, Trudie Goodwin, who is also a member of
OL,11,CFriends of the Earth.                  
OL,13, "There is far too much traffic on our  
OL,14, streets andCwe are all suffering.      
OL,16,C"Pollution, global warming, noise      
OL,17, disturbances and congestion are but a  
OL,18, few of the problems we face. I don't   
OL,19, like them so why should I accept them?"
