OL,5,CTRUDIE GOODWIN                Wx}}b4  
OL,6,                             W`~    
OL,7, "There'sCno point going offGabout an   
OL,8, issue if you don't act on it," stresses
OL,9, Trudie Goodwin.                        
OL,11, "I know it's not much butCevery little 
OL,12,CcountsG- even my efforts to walk my    
OL,13, daughters Jessica and Eleanor to school
OL,14, rather than rely on the car.           
OL,16,C"As a custodian of this planet.GI want 
OL,17, to leave it in a decent condition for  
OL,18, my children - the next custodians - and
OL,19, I hope they will feel the same."       
